<title>SOUTH AFRICA: BA reinstates cancelled S.African flights.</title>
<headline>BA reinstates cancelled S.African flights.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-07-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>British Airways Plc said it had reinstated flights cancelled earlier on Tuesday in the aftermath of last week's 72-hour strike by cabin crew, following crew rescheduling.</p>
<p>BA had cancelled services from London to Johnnesburg on Wednesday night and to Cape Town on Thursday night, and from Johannesburg to London on Thursday night and from Cape Town on Friday.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
